Лиганды для докинга¶

In [24]:
smiles = ['c1cccc(O)c1', 'c1c(O)ccc(O)c1','c1(O)cc(c2ccccc2)cc(O)c1']
mols= []
images =[]

for s in smiles:
    m = oddt.toolkit.readstring('smi', s)
    if not m.OBMol.Has3D(): 
        m.make3D(forcefield='mmff94', steps=150)
        m.removeh()
        m.OBMol.AddPolarHydrogens()

    mols.append(m)
    ###with print m.OBMol.Has3D() was found that:
    ### deep copy needed to keep 3D , write svg make mols flat
    images.append((SVG(copy.deepcopy(m).write('svg'))))

display_svg(*images)

for i,r in enumerate(res):
    hbs = len(oddt.interactions.hbonds(prot,r)[1])
    stack= len(oddt.interactions.pi_stacking(prot,r)[1])
    phob = len(oddt.interactions.hydrophobic_contacts(prot,r)[1])
    print "%4d%10s%8s%8s%8s%4d%4d%4d" %(
        i,r.formula, r.data['vina_affinity'],  r.data['vina_rmsd_ub'], r.residues[0].name, hbs, stack, phob
    )

smiles = ['OC(=O)NC1C(C(C(OC1O)CO)O)O',               #OH
          '[NH3+]C(=O)NC1C(C(C(OC1O)CO)O)O',          #NH3+
          'C(=O)NC1C(C(C(OC1O)CO)O)O',                #H
          'C1=CC=[C]C=C1C(=O)NC1C(C(C(OC1O)CO)O)O',   #PH
          '[O-]C(=O)C(=O)NC1C(C(C(OC1O)CO)O)O']       #COO  
names = ['OH', 'NH3+', 'H', 'PH', 'COO-']
mols= []
images =[]

for s in smiles:
    m = oddt.toolkit.readstring('smi', s)
    if not m.OBMol.Has3D(): 
        m.make3D(forcefield='mmff94', steps=150)
        m.removeh()
        m.OBMol.AddPolarHydrogens()

    mols.append(m)
    ###with print m.OBMol.Has3D() was found that:
    ### deep copy needed to keep 3D , write svg make mols flat
    images.append((SVG(copy.deepcopy(m).write('svg'))))

display_svg(*images)

In [62]:
results = []

formula_to_name = {
    "C7H13NO6": "H",
    "C7H13NO7": "OH",
    "C7H16N2O6": "NH3+",
    "C8H13NO8": "COO",
    "C13H17NO6": "PH",
}

for i, r in enumerate(res):
    results.append({"name": formula_to_name[r.formula], "affinity": float(r.data['vina_affinity'])})

results = pd.DataFrame(results).groupby(by=["name"]).mean().sort_values("affinity")
results
